com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.zone

Class ZoneGetResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.discoverydns.dnsapiclient.command.zone.ZoneGetResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ZoneCreateResponse, ZoneUpdateResourceRecordsResponse, ZoneUpdateResponse

    public class ZoneGetResponse
extends Object
    Response object received by the DNSAPIClient from the DNSAPI server subsequently to the sending of a ZoneGetCommand, describing the details of the retrieved Zone. A Zone, belonging to an Account, will be managed by the DNSAPI architecture for domain names resolution purpose.
    Author:
    Chris Wright
